<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.183386>
    bibo:endPage "52" ;
    bibo:journal "Zootaxa" ;
    bibo:startPage "43" ;
    bibo:volume "1850" ;
    dc:creator "Kito, Kenji; Ohyama, Yoshikuni" ;
    dc:date "2008" ;
    dc:title "Rhabditid nematodes found from a rocky coast contaminated with treated wastewater of Casey Station in East Antarctica, with a description of a new species of Dolichorhabditis Andrássy, 1983 (Nematoda: Rhabditidae)" ;
    fabio:hasPart <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.183388>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.183389> ;
    a fabio:JournalArticle .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.183388>
    dc:description "FIGURE 2. Dolichorhabditis tereticorpus sp. n. Female (holotype ZIHU 3317; left side view, except F in right side view): A) Entire body. B) Anterior region. C) Stoma region. D) Posterior region of pharynx. E) Reproductive system. F) Anterior region of anterior ovary. G) Vulval region. Lateral field indistinct, only three longitudinal lines observed. H) Posterior region. Scales: A: 100 µm; B: 20 µm; C, D, F – H: 10 µm; E: 50 µm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/183388/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.183389>
    dc:description "FIGURE 3. Dolichorhabditis tereticorpus sp. n. Female (A – C, holotype ZIHU 3317; D, ZIHU 3320; left side view): A) Middle of pharynx. Arrow: junction of corpus and isthmus; nr, nerve ring. B) Anterior branch of reproductive system: ova, ovary; ovi, oviduct; s, spermatheca; u, uterus. C, D) Rectum: r, rectum; r gl, rectal gland cells. Scales: A, B: 20 µm; C, D: 10 µm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/183389/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

